MetaTile: Integrate with Salesforce | CRM Automation | Cyclr
MetaDescription: Create unique Salesforce Integrations with Cyclr's easy to use, drag & drop automation workflow builder, and let your users benefit from process automation.
Content:
Cyclr’s integration platform, with easy to use drag and drop builder, allows you to create integration with Salesforce that lets your users make most of their CRM customer data; automatically streamline business processes in no time.

Let your users integrate their Salesforce data with their favourite web apps to automate marketing, create bespoke sales workflows and manage contact integrity with less resources and time.
